State of Florida, Plaintiff in Error, v. Hugh C. Bethea, Defendant in Error. Park Trammell, Attorney General, and H. S. Phillips, for Plaintiff in Error; J. W. Burton, for Defendant in Error.

Writ of error to a judgment of the Circuit Court for the County of DeSoto.

Writ of error dismissed on prascipe of counsel for Plaintiff in Error.
